entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've compelted the Weed Whacker Foliage Requisition.
entries.journal_entry_description: Pull weeds around Nym's Stronghold, but hurry!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find the paddle cacti type weed and pull them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Pull the weeds growing low to the ground. Sometimes these weeds have blueish fruit.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find the flowering cacti type weed and pull them.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find the short yellow weeds with small pods and pull them.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Find the tall stalk type weeds and pull them.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Fullfill the requisition by pulling weeds around Nym's Stronghold
entries.task06_task_display_string_1: You've pulled all the tall stalk weeds.
entries.task06_task_display_string_2: You've pulled all the yellow pod weeds.
entries.task06_task_display_string_3: You've pulled all the flowering cacti weeds.
entries.task06_task_display_string_4: You've pulled all the low growing weeds.
entries.task06_task_display_string_5: You've pulled all the paddle cacti weeds.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: I see you have fulfilled the weed quota. You can drop them in the dumpster. A waypoint has been provided.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Dispose of the weeds at the waypoint provided.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return to Machado for your payment.
